  "reference_number": "VEN0015",
  "remarks": "\nXavier Antonio Moreno Reyes previously (until 12 June 2020) served as Secretary General of the National Electoral Council (CNE). There are reasonable grounds to suspect he that Xavier Antonio Moreno Reyes (1) has been involved in undermining democracy and repressing the democratic opposition in Venezuela by signing, facilitating, legitimising and giving credibility to signing off CNE decisions, (including those which facilitated the establishment of the National Constituent Assembly and manipulation of the electoral process), and (2) has acted on behalf of, and/or at the direction of, and/or in association with, the former President of the CNE, Tibisay Lucena Ramirez. \n",
